Kuthiwa uxoshiwe ejimini futhi udingisiwe kuwo wonke amajimu ukuthi angaphinde abonakale khona ngenxa yokukhohlakala. Bakhala ngokuthi isenzo sakhe sizodala ukuthi abesifazane bazizwe bengakhululekile ngesikhathi bejima. Kuthiwa lo wesifazane ubejima eshona evumbuka indoda imbuka izinqe kubonakala ukuthi akusekho okunye ekwenzayo amehlo asethe njo kuyena. Ibinganakile ngesikhathi omunye umuntu eyithwebula ngeselula ingasacwayizi ibuka izinqe. Kubonakale isandla sayo sinyakaza ngokukhulu ukushesha esikhindini sayo kubonakala ukuthi kukhulu ematasa ngakho. Ibiphethe iselula ngesinye isandla ibe imboze ngethawula isingezansi egila kuso umkhuba. Lo obethwebula ufake ezinkundleni zokuxhumana ethi kufanele ivele obala le ndoda. Kuthiwa ayipholisanga maseko ijimu edumile kuleli, yamkhomba indlela lo mlisa yanqamula inkontileka yakhe yokujima. Abantu ezinkundleni zokuxhumana bebeyigxeka le ndoda bethi kufanele ihlazwe ngesenzo sayo ngoba singamanyala.